content: [TextBlock(text="[2025 | Age 22] Just landed back in the concrete jungle of NYC, but my heart's still at the serene slopes of Mount Fuji. The city skyline feels so different now, like it's missing the peaceful silence of Tokyo. #CultureShock #Homecomings", type='text')]

[TextBlock(text='[2025 | Age 22] NYC feels like a different planet after Asia. Every corner here is bustling, but I miss the quiet moments sketching in Tokyo. Thinking about starting a digital sketchbook project, blending tech with traditional art. Any artists out there interested in a collab? #ArtMeetsTech', type='text')]
